Consider one agent 
\begin_inset Formula $A,$
\end_inset

 for example, agent 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 is `chicken'.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $(1,...,s,...,S)$
\end_inset

