\end_inset

 is a consequence function or outcomes, which is dependend both on the state
 of nature 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 and your action 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

.
 For example, 
\begin_inset Formula $c($
\end_inset

