 For example, 
\begin_inset Formula $p($
\end_inset

 car on the road
\begin_inset Formula $)=0.7$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Most of the time, one will take action 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 as given and denote 
